com.psa.rxlightstreamer.core

Class RxSubscription<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psa.rxlightstreamer.core.RxSubscription<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestSubscription

    public abstract class RxSubscription<T>
extends java.lang.Object

    This class represents a subscription. A subscription can be of one of the types of SubscriptionType and will link with an adapter of the adapter set given in the RxLightStreamerClient.

    The class is meant to be extended in order to implement the items and the fields that belong to the class as well as the conversion from com.lightstreamer.client.ItemUpdate to the type that the subscription returns.

    The updates from the subscription come from the subscription observable.
